{"tid":1636880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"近期好多狗打去附近消防局叫人清路障","createTime":"2019-10-07T23:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:53:35.000Z","uid":115769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b5d166413e50728f44a66df4cda8e410e9fe1b","tid":1636880,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"朋友現職，無accout,代post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaEFhPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaEFhPi.jpg&h=482bd1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSggAAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSggAAZ.jpg&h=af813e88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a514f5809650a7e59d64c40aeff88724f4a315a8","tid":1636880,"uid":61484,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"好撚懶<br />\n淨係打人就得<br />\n其他野全部唔做<br />\n<br />\n捉賊(休班狗)唔做，捉黑社會(休班狗)唔做，清rb唔做，開file 收投訴唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d3ba79a2ca20d868af7d2867fd5cd22153f296","tid":1636880,"uid":9548,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"支持消防無視與自己職責無關既一切東西"},{"pid":"49368a22ca9632a6ee7fef72d7ea0ea4053d720d","tid":1636880,"uid":244034,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"D裝甲車水炮車廢架，要人做埋你果份，人哋要加人工又係度嘈亂巴閉"},{"pid":"bd12d9bddc7df2bcefe79674cf19a0e54f910e0d","tid":1636880,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a514f5809650a7e59d64c40aeff88724f4a315a8","tid":1636880,"uid":61484,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"好撚懶<br />\n淨係打人就得<br />\n其他野全部唔做<br />\n<br />\n捉賊(休班狗)唔做，捉黑社會(休班狗)唔做，清rb唔做，開file 收投訴唔做<img src=\"/as